subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament (Women)
College Athletics
Basketball
lead_paragraph: Connecticut has dominated women’s college basketball this season, but even if the Huskies win another N.C.A.A. title, many believe they are nowhere near as great as their 2002 championship team.
